----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note on the included U-Boot SPL binary
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The file precompiled/u-boot-sunxi-with-spl.bin is a build of Das U-Boot
(https://source.denx.de/u-boot/u-boot), which is licensed under the
GNU General Public License v2.0 or later. The source is publicly available
upstream and the build recipe is documented in the README; the included
binary is provided as a convenience.

The included BL31 image used during build comes from Debian's
arm-trusted-firmware package (https://www.trustedfirmware.org/projects/tf-a/),
licensed BSD-3-Clause.

The included device-tree files (precompiled/*.dtb, source/*.dts) derive from
the mainline Linux kernel and are licensed under the GPL-2.0 or MIT (dual).
